Author: fishonthesun
Text: If you feel it coming up on it's own, dont try to stop it. I actually threw up earlier and I felt a bit better. Your body knows if something in it should not be in it, so trust that. Just give your body and not your brain the reins today. Congrats on not purging for a week, I'm also at a week!!! Its not easy but we're doing it so I'm proud of both of us   Good luck
